      "message": "I am not sure about prompt - it might be annoying for those who need it to be public.\n\ncould you elaborate on the hesitation of making -realm required?\n\nDevelopers will not use `rdb stream` directly. This tool is too low-level. For example in case of Chromium, `rdb stream` will be invoked by Dirks\u0027 test wrappers. For them, passing -realm chromium/public would be trivial.",
